    "Both phases rely on the possibility to train the language model on very large amounts of data, the content of which is not transparent.",
    "26 This way of training raises a series of questions.",
    "Firstly, the use of large datasets that have been created starting from libraries of crawled data and then refined using different filters, some of which are unaccounted for, raises the question of whether information fed to LLMs during training is biased, to the disadvantage of different groups in society.",
